| 3 | esbuild.js | Potentially externalize filetomarkdown |

### Implementation Order

1. npm install filetomarkdown, test bundling
2. Create types/indexer-types.ts
3. Create converter.ts
4. Modify indexer.ts with conversion pipeline
5. Update quick pick label
6. Test with sample files
7. Fix esbuild issues if any
8. Run vsce package to verify

## 9. Deployment Considerations

* filetomarkdown bundled in VSIX via esbuild
* Verify extension size increase < 5MB
* Rollback: revert indexer.ts to md-only version
* No data migration needed (KB entries are additive)

